happened to us.

16:44.804 --> 16:47.438
We made mistakes and
we learned from them.

16:47.440 --> 16:49.140
What about Rarity?

16:49.142 --> 16:51.075
Are we really supposed to
believe she learned anything

16:51.077 --> 16:52.476
she wrote in there?

16:52.478 --> 16:54.712
That's why you
gotta be Team Dash!

16:54.714 --> 16:57.148
She's the only one who didn't
really need to learn anything

16:57.150 --> 16:59.450
because she was already so cool!

16:59.452 --> 17:02.353
Twilight was better
before she got wings.

17:02.355 --> 17:04.622
Fluttershy is just
so painfully shy,

17:04.624 --> 17:06.724
