I mean, come on!

17:06.726 --> 17:11.128
[angry chatter]

17:11.130 --> 17:13.064
Wait a minute, everypony!

17:13.066 --> 17:15.733
Are Pinkie Pie and
Applejack related or what?

17:15.735 --> 17:22.306
[angry shouting]

17:22.308 --> 17:23.474
Listen to me!

17:23.476 --> 17:24.708
LISTEN TO ME!

17:24.710 --> 17:26.777
[silence]

