<i>♪ Our flaws help to make</i>
<i>us special ♪</i>

17:40.760 --> 17:43.594
<i>♪ They bond us and</i>
<i>keep us strong ♪</i>

17:43.596 --> 17:46.097
<i>♪ Our flaws are what</i>
<i>brought us together ♪</i>

17:46.099 --> 17:49.233
<i>♪ So stop acting like</i>
<i>something's wrong. ♪</i>

