<i>♪ Ponies think I'm all</i>
<i>bubbles and laughter ♪</i>

18:55.801 --> 18:58.202
<i>♪ That I don't seem sincere ♪</i>

18:58.204 --> 19:00.404
<i>♪ I might joke around a</i>
<i>little too much ♪</i>

19:00.406 --> 19:03.307
<i>♪ But I'm just so</i>
<i>happy you're here. ♪</i>

