<i>♪ It took me a while</i>
<i>to be confident ♪</i>

19:05.945 --> 19:08.812
<i>♪ To really come out</i>
<i>of my shell ♪</i>

19:08.814 --> 19:11.315
<i>♪ But no pony has</i>
<i>to be perfect ♪</i>

19:11.317 --> 19:14.485
<i>♪ By now don't you know us</i>
