<i>♪ So tell me what</i>
<i>flaws you got too ♪</i>

19:32.605 --> 19:35.839
<i>♪ Cause I still like</i>
<i>what's flawed about you. ♪</i>

19:35.841 --> 19:39.310
♪♪

19:42.815 --> 19:44.481
So you see, everypony?

19:44.483 --> 19:46.650
None of us ever
claimed to be perfect.

19:46.652 --> 19:47.985
Without our flaws,

19:47.987 --> 19:50.621
there wouldn't be any
friendship lessons to learn.

19:50.623 --> 19:52.423
Without our flaws...

19:52.425 --> 19:55.626
... there probably wouldn't
be any friendships at all.

19:55.628 --> 20:00.865
[loud chatter]

20:04.670 --> 20:05.436
[slam]

20:05.438 --> 20:06.804
[sighs]

20:06.806 --> 20:08.939
So that just
happened.

20:08.941 --> 20:11.775
Girls! I found two ponies
who have something

20:11.777 --> 20:13.611
I think you should hear.

20:13.613 --> 20:18.282
Um... we just wanted to say
thank you to all of you.

20:18.284 --> 20:20.384
Yeah. Our friendship...

20:20.386 --> 20:23.520
well, we were having trouble
until we read your journal.

20:23.522 --> 20:26.724
It showed us that friends can go
through all sorts of tough times

20:26.726 --> 20:28.959
and come through
stronger than before.

20:28.961 --> 20:31.662
It's made us better friends
than we've ever been.

20:31.664 --> 20:33.030
Really?

20:33.032 --> 20:35.499
Mm-hm.

20:35.501 --> 20:38.602
Oh, I can't tell you how
much it means to hear that.

20:38.604 --> 20:40.638
Thank you for telling us.

20:40.640 --> 20:42.506
We've had a tough
couple of days.

20:42.508 --> 20:44.808
But knowing we've helped
fillies like you...

20:44.810 --> 20:47.645
It makes everything we've
been through worth it.

20:47.647 --> 20:48.946
Absolutely.

20:48.948 --> 20:52.616
Fads come and go;
friendship is forever.

20:52.618 --> 20:55.786
There are worse things than
not being able to do anything

20:55.788 --> 20:58.022
without being told I'm awesome.

20:58.024 --> 21:00.891
And we can't change the way
other ponies think about us,

21:00.893 --> 21:03.694
but we can change how
we let it affect us.

21:03.696 --> 21:05.730
Or how we don't
let it affect us.

21:07.733 --> 21:10.334
Go ahead. Laugh!

21:10.336 --> 21:18.909
[laughter]

21:20.446 --> 21:23.881
Reckon we still have to
deal with them, don't we?

21:23.883 --> 21:26.717
[angry chatter]

21:27.853 --> 21:29.754
Stay in the friendship
moment, Applejack.

21:29.822 --> 21:31.889
They can wait a little longer.
